miBRAIN snRNA-seq Pipeline
==========================
Single-nucleus RNA-seq processing, cell type annotation, pseudobulk differential
expression, and gene set enrichment analysis for A53T α-synuclein iPSC-derived
brain organoids (miBrains) across APOE3 and APOE4 backgrounds vs isogenic controls.

Study:   Cholesterol-mediated Lysosomal Dysfunction in APOE4 Astrocytes Promotes
         α-Synuclein Pathology in miBrains, a Human iPSC-derived Brain Tissue
         Louise A. Mesentier-Louro*, Camille Goldman*, Sebastian Gaese,
         Alice Buonfiglioli, Dimitrios Kyriakis, Ashley Harlock, Alain Ndayisaba,
         Emily R. Sartori, John Fullard, Abigail Uchitelev, Braxton R. Schuldt,
         Rikki B. Rooklin, Jonathan Barra-Carrasco, Jose Bravo-Cordero,
         Panos Roussos, Vikram Khurana, Joel W. Blanchard  (* equal contribution)
Computational single-cell analysis: Dimitrios Kyriakis (dimitrios.kyriakis@mssm.edu)
Lead contact: Joel W. Blanchard (joel.blanchard@mssm.edu)
Data:    https://cells-test.gi.ucsc.edu/?ds=mibrain  (UCSC Cell Browser)

Samples: 6 libraries — Blanchard-wt-{a,b}, Blanchard-A53T-E3-{a,b}, Blanchard-A53T-E4-{a,b}
Contrasts: E3 vs Control | E4 vs Control | E4 vs E3 | A53T (pooled) vs Control


Pipeline stages
---------------

FASTQ files  (6 samples, 2 replicates per genotype)
   │
   ▼
[1] 01_cellranger_count.sh          Cell Ranger 9.0.1 — FASTQ → filtered .h5 matrices
    02_cellranger_annotate.sh        [OPTIONAL] 10x Cloud automated cell annotation
   │
   ▼  filtered_feature_bc_matrix.h5 (per sample)
[2] 03_qc_preprocessing_annotation.py    MAD-based QC · doublet removal · log1p norm
    └── utils.py                         signature scores · Harmony batch integration
                                         Leiden clustering · pseudobulk annotation
   │
   ▼  miBRAIN_annotated.h5ad
[3] 04_annotation_concordance_AMPPD.py   Pseudobulk Pearson + Spearman correlation
    └── utils_correlation.py             miBRAIN vs AMP-PD postmortem brain reference
   │
   ▼  AMPPD_*_Correlation.csv
[4] 05_pseudobulk_de_dreamlet.R          Pseudobulk DE (dreamlet 1.9) · variance
                                         partition · marker genes · fgsea (KEGG/GO)
   │
   ▼  miBRAIN_CLASS_cova_Diff.rds  ·  Summary_DEGs_*.csv  ·  *_Enrichment.csv
[5] 06_gsea_clusterProfiler.R            Targeted GSEA (gseGO) — curated GO sets
                                         for Neurons and Astrocytes


Running the pipeline
--------------------

# 1. Alignment
bash 01_cellranger_count.sh \
    --reference /path/to/refdata-gex-GRCh38-2024-A \
    --fastqs    /path/to/fastqs \
    --outdir    /path/to/01_counts \
    --cores 8 --mem 64

bash 02_cellranger_annotate.sh \          # optional
    --count-dir /path/to/01_counts \
    --outdir    /path/to/02_annotate \
    --token     /path/to/txg/credentials

# 2. QC, normalisation, clustering, annotation
python 03_qc_preprocessing_annotation.py \
    --cellranger-dir /path/to/01_counts \
    --outdir         /path/to/03_qc \
    --ensembl-csv    /path/to/human_ensembl_metadata.csv \
    --mitocarta-csv  /path/to/Human.MitoCarta3.0.csv \
    --ref-agg-dir    /path/to/reference_aggregations \
    --annot-h5ad     /path/to/miBRAIN_annotated.h5ad

# 3. Cross-dataset annotation concordance
python 04_annotation_concordance_AMPPD.py \
    --query-h5ad /path/to/miBRAIN_annotated.h5ad \
    --ref-h5ad   /path/to/AMPPD_reference.h5ad \
    --outdir     /path/to/04_correlation \
    --figure-dir /path/to/04_correlation/figures

# 4. Pseudobulk DE + fgsea
Rscript 05_pseudobulk_de_dreamlet.R \
    --workdir  /path/to/05_dreamlet \
    --prefix   miBRAIN_ \
    --kegg-gmt /path/to/c2.cp.kegg.v7.5.1.symbols.gmt \
    --gobp-gmt /path/to/c5.go.bp.v7.5.1.symbols.gmt \
    --gomf-gmt /path/to/c5.go.mf.v7.5.1.symbols.gmt \
    --outdir   /path/to/05_dreamlet/output

# 5. Targeted GSEA
Rscript 06_gsea_clusterProfiler.R \
    --dreamlet-rds /path/to/miBRAIN_CLASS_cova_Diff.rds \
    --outdir       /path/to/06_gsea


Script-to-result mapping
------------------------

Script                               Output files                                 Figures
-----------------------------------  -------------------------------------------  --------------------------------
01_cellranger_count.sh               filtered_feature_bc_matrix.h5 (per sample)   —
02_cellranger_annotate.sh            cell_types.csv (per sample)                  —
03_qc_preprocessing_annotation.py   miBRAIN_annotated.h5ad                        UMAP · cell type composition
                                     doublets.png · QC histograms                  barplots · QC panels
04_annotation_concordance_AMPPD.py  AMPPD_Pearson_Correlation.csv                 Annotation concordance heatmap
                                     AMPPD_Spearman_Correlation.csv
05_pseudobulk_de_dreamlet.R         miBRAIN_CLASS_cova_Diff.rds                   Variance partition · voom plots
                                     Summary_DEGs_E3vsCntrl.csv                    Volcano panels · cell type
                                     Summary_DEGs_E4vsCntrl.csv                    specificity heatmap · pathway
                                     Summary_DEGs_E4vsE3.csv                       bubble plots (fgsea)
                                     E3vsCntrl_Neurons_GOBP_Enrichment.csv
                                     markers_raw.rds · markers_clean.rds
06_gsea_clusterProfiler.R           GSEA enrichment objects (per pathway)          GSEA 3-panel plots (Neurons,
                                                                                    Astrocytes)


Key parameters
--------------

Parameter              Value           Script       Purpose
---------------------  --------------  -----------  ----------------------------------------
n_top_genes            6 000           03           HVG selection (cell_ranger, batch-aware)
n_pcs                  30              03           PCA components
k_graph                100             03           kNN graph neighbours (L2 distance)
leiden_res             0.10 / 0.20     03           Leiden clustering resolutions
MAD_k                  4               03 utils     MAD multiplier for nUMI / nGene QC
percent_mito           5 %             03 utils     Mitochondrial read cutoff
harmony_batch          Sample          03           Harmony batch correction key
seed                   20210224        03 / 04      Random seed (Python)
seed                   42              06           Random seed (R)
CONTRASTS              E3vsCntrl       05           dreamlet linear contrasts
                       E4vsCntrl
                       E4vsE3
                       A53TvsCtrl
BiocParallel workers   12              05           SnowParam CPU workers
nPermSimple (fgsea)    1 000           05           fgsea permutations
nPermSimple (gseGO)    10 000          06           clusterProfiler GSEA permutations
minGSSize              5               06           Minimum gene set size
maxGSSize              1 000           06           Maximum gene set size


Cell types annotated
--------------------

Leiden clusters (res 0.20) annotated by pseudobulk Pearson correlation against:
  2025_HgOrgAtlas · snMultiome developing human neocortex · AMP-PD freeze 2
  (Class + Subclass) · PsychAD (Class + Subclass)

Final labels: MC · Neurons · NPC · IP · Astrocytes · Neuroepithelium
              Endothelial · PC · IPC-Glia · Microglia


External files (must be provided at runtime)
--------------------------------------------

File                            Source
------------------------------  ----------------------------------------------------------
refdata-gex-GRCh38-2024-A/     https://www.10xgenomics.com/support/software/cell-ranger
human_ensembl_metadata.csv      https://www.ensembl.org/biomart  (GRCh38, Ensembl 109+)
                                  required columns: Gene name · Gene stable ID ·
                                  Chromosome/scaffold name · Gene type
Human.MitoCarta3.0.csv          https://www.broadinstitute.org/mitocarta
MSigDB GMT files v7.5.1         https://www.gsea-msigdb.org/gsea/downloads.jsp
                                  c2.cp.kegg · c5.go.bp · c5.go.mf
AMPPD reference .h5ad           T. Clarence et al. / AMP-PD consortium
pge (Pegasus Extras)            Private package — contact corresponding author
                                  (provides pb_agg_by_cluster, pearson_corr,
                                  spearman_corr, scanpy_hvf_h5ad, qc_boundary)


Environment
-----------

Cell Ranger  9.0.1
Python       3.10+
R            4.3+   Bioconductor 3.18+

Python packages:
  pegasuspy · pegasusio · scanpy · anndata · numpy · pandas · scipy
  seaborn · matplotlib · adjustText · session_info

R packages:
  dreamlet 1.9 · variancePartition · zenith · crumblr · zellkonverter
  SingleCellExperiment · BiocParallel · Seurat 4/5 · clusterProfiler 4.x
  enrichplot · fgsea · org.Hs.eg.db · GOSemSim · presto · dittoSeq
  ggplot2 · tidyverse · cowplot · ggrepel · aplot · ggtree · qvalue · optparse

Session information (exact package versions) is printed at the start of every
script via session_info.show() (Python) and sessionInfo() (R).


